Build Instructions


Note: 1) This package has been built successfully on Ubuntu with gcc 4.5.2.
      2) Compiling this package on platforms other than Ubuntu may have unexpected results.

How to build:
1. unzip XR500-V2.2.0.4_gpl_src.tar.bz2.zip
2. tar -jxvf XR500-V2.2.0.4_gpl_src.tar.bz2
3. cd XR500-V2.2.0.4_gpl_src
4. cp configs/defconfig-xr500 .config
5. make V=99
6. the final images is './bin/ipq806x/XR500-V2.2.0.4.img'

User may upgrade to this image using the XR500 GUI "Router Upgrade" page.
